<item>
            <title>[NET-195] Ntpv3Impl attempts double-checked locking</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NET-195</link>
                <project id="12310487" key="NET">Commons Net</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The NtpV3Impl#getDatagramPacket() method implements double-checked locking, which is known not to work.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The initial &quot;if (dp == null)&quot; condition should be removed; once this is done, the synch block could be removed and the method synchronized instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
